# CANSAT 2026 – ESP32 GPIO Pin Mapping

## Sensors and Peripherals

| Function                | Device / Module       | ESP32 Pin | Notes |
|-------------------------|------------------------|-----------|-------|
| **Hall sensor output**  | SS49E (U3)             | GPIO34    | ADC1_CH6 (analog) |
| **Battery voltage sense** | R1–R2 divider         | GPIO35    | ADC1_CH7 (analog), 2:1 divider |
| **I²C SDA**             | BMP280 (U2)            | GPIO32    | I²C bus |
| **I²C SCL**             | BMP280 (U2)            | GPIO33    | I²C bus |
| **HX711 DATA**          | HX711 (U4)             | GPIO22    | Not a boot pin |
| **HX711 CLOCK**         | HX711 (U4)             | GPIO27    | -
| **SPI CS (SD card)**    | MicroSD (P1)           | GPIO5     | VSPI CS |
| **SPI SCK**             | MicroSD (P1)           | GPIO18    | VSPI SCK |
| **SPI MOSI**            | MicroSD (P1)           | GPIO23    | VSPI MOSI |
| **SPI MISO**            | MicroSD (P1)           | GPIO19    | VSPI MISO |
| **LoRa RX → ESP TX**    | WLR089U0 (U5)          | GPIO25    | UART for LoRa |
| **LoRa TX → ESP RX**    | WLR089U0 (U5)          | GPIO26    | UART for LoRa |
| **GPS TX → ESP RX2**    | NEO-8M (External)      | GPIO16    | UART2 RX |
| **GPS RX → ESP TX2**    | NEO-8M (External)      | GPIO17    | UART2 TX |

## Power Paths

| Function | Node | Notes |
|----------|------|--------|
| Battery + | Bat+ | From Li-Ion cell via SK-12D02 switch |
| Battery Sense Divider | R1 (100k) – R2 (100k) | Bat+ → R1 → ADC35 → R2 → GND |
| 3.3 V Rail | VCC | ESP32 regulator output |

